transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra, I score blue, how can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, this is Charles Henderson, and I want to go ahead and reorder my prescription.

Speaker 1: Okay, Charles, can I get your date of birth, please?

Speaker 2: November 6, 1959.

Speaker 1: Okay, Charles, your prescription was for the quantity of 25 100-milligram Viagra AGV?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Do you want me to put a refill in for the same order?

Speaker 2: Oh, yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay, and you're still at 6500 Plantation Court, Mobile, Alabama?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: All right, I'll put that through right now.

Speaker 2: Can I get that shipped express?

Speaker 1: You can, yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, so on your card, it would be $23 or $33, excuse me, $28 or $38, so today or next day air?

Speaker 1: Why don't we just do two-day?

Speaker 2: All right, two-day, okay.

Speaker 1: So on your card, you will see two charges.

Speaker 2: One will be for the prescription itself, the other will be $28 for the two-day, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right, I went ahead and put that through for you, and you're all set.

Speaker 1: Okay, thanks, I appreciate you.

Speaker 2: You got it. Happy to help. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Okay, you too, man. Thank you. Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
